.name
Angie
.description
ANother Great Intuition Enhancer commodity that offers about
100 Intuition related actions you may assign to multiple
arbitrary hotkeys.  Arbitrary DOS commands and input event
data may be assigned to the hotkeys too.  Furthermore, Angie
includes automatic window hunting, auto ActiveWinTask priority
increment, 'TWA' type window remembering, auto DefPubScreen
definition, etc.  Angie comes with a comfortable Intuition
user interface.
.fullname
ANother Great Intuition Enhancer
.short
Intuition enhancing commodity.
.type
WorkBench Tool
.version
1.6
